rows.label: qst103903_msg0001
rows.name: 'Sup, got something to send?

rows.label: qst103903_msg0002
rows.name:
The amount of money that arrived
was way too small?

rows.label: qst103903_msg0003
rows.name:
What d'you think I'm doing, cooking
the books with the handling fees?
Is that what you're saying?

rows.label: qst103903_msg0004
rows.name:
It's true I don't always send the
money right away. I wait until you've
deposited 90,000G or so.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0005
rows.name:
But that's to keep the handling fees
down, not up. Iyasaki's a long way off,
so it's pricey to make lots of trips.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0006
rows.name:
The Avaritia Trade Guild skims off
2% right off the bat, you know. Send
90,000G, they take nearly two grand.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0007
rows.name:
So each delivery that leaves here
should come to 88,200G.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0008
rows.name:
From here, the next stop would be
Hugh at the couriers in Torigo.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0009
rows.name:
There's no direct passage to Liberalitas
from here so we gotta send it via him.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0010
rows.name:
Check with Hugh in Torigo.
Maybe it's his fees that are
eating into your savings.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0011
rows.name:
If there's something fishy going on,
I'll see what I can do to help.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0012
rows.name: You're one of my best customers!

rows.label: qst103903_msg0101
rows.name:
You might think some of these fees are
a little high, but y'know what they say.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0102
rows.name:
"If you're smiling at the price, then
somebody else is crying."

rows.label: qst103903_msg0103
rows.name:
That's no way to do business.
Better if everyone gets a fair
price for an honest day's work.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0201
rows.name:
You want to set up a direct shipping
route between Avaritia and Iyasaki?

rows.label: qst103903_msg0202
rows.name:
Hoo boy.
There just isn't enough going to
Iyasaki to justify a daily trip.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0203
rows.name:
But since it's you...
I'll see what I can do.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0204
rows.name:
Right, if it's once a week, I think we
should be able to work something out
for Ysheva Harbor.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0205
rows.name:
Wait, wait. Hang on a sec.
There's a problem.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0206
rows.name:
Unfortunately, I don't have access
to the kinda long-haul Divine Beast ship
you'd need.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0207
rows.name:
If you can provide the ship.
I'll set up the shipping route.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0208
rows.name:
If you want to buy a ship,
you should talk to Pookapoo
on Goldmund Flight Deck.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0209
rows.name:
If you'd rather rent, then
you want Umon in Gula
Province.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0210
rows.name:
Sounds like a lot of work...
But it's for a good cause, eh?
Helping your home town and all that.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0301
rows.name:
If you want to buy a ship,
you should talk to Pookapoo
on Goldmund Flight Deck.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0302
rows.name:
If you'd rather rent, then
you want Umon in Gula
Province.

rows.label: qst103903_msg0303
rows.name: If anyone can do it, it's you!
